129
00:06:04,897 --> 00:06:10,001
Whereas there are thousands of pet partners therapy animal teams serving communities across the United States.

130
00:06:10,542 --> 00:06:15,186
And whereas pet partners has designated April 30 as National Therapy Animal Day.

131
00:06:15,886 --> 00:06:24,593
And whereas scientific research shows that interacting with therapy animals can reduce stress, relieve depression, slow the heart rate, lower blood pressure and strengthen the immune system.

132
00:06:25,270 --> 00:06:32,511
And whereas therapy animal teams in the city of Medford play an essential role in improving human health and well-being through the human animal bond.

133
00:06:33,071 --> 00:06:41,973
And whereas therapy animal teams interact with a variety of people in our community, including veterans, seniors, patients, students, and those approaching end of life.

134
00:06:42,673 --> 00:06:48,934
