135
00:06:49,934 --> 00:06:54,015
And whereas we encourage more pet owners to consider becoming pet partners, volunteers,

136
00:06:54,551 --> 00:06:58,272
to help our community by creating greater access to meaningful therapy animal visits.

137
00:06:58,872 --> 00:07:09,715
Now, therefore, be it resolved by the Medford City Council that we acknowledge April 30th, 2024 as National Animal Therapy Day and encourage our citizens to celebrate our therapy animals and their human handlers.

138
00:07:10,675 --> 00:07:16,657
Be it further resolved that we publicly salute the service of therapy animal teams in our community and in communities across the nation.

139
00:07:17,742 --> 00:07:24,545
